00:55:40.597 --> 00:55:42.057
Did you two fight?

832
00:55:42.551 --> 00:55:44.960
No. Why would we fight?

833
00:55:46.806 --> 00:55:47.636
Lee Eun-ho!

834
00:55:48.306 --> 00:55:49.849
Why'd you come when you're busy?

835
00:55:49.892 --> 00:55:50.852
What are you doing here?

836
00:55:51.483 --> 00:55:52.259
Me?

837
00:55:53.813 --> 00:55:54.824
Eating soup.

838
00:56:02.022 --> 00:56:02.816
What is it?

839
00:56:03.028 --> 00:56:03.847
What?

840
00:56:07.779 --> 00:56:08.707
Forget it.

841
00:56:09.173 --> 00:56:10.348
Happy New Year.

842
00:56:12.255 --> 00:56:13.006
Hey!

843
00:56:13.138 --> 00:56:14.660
Don't yell at me.

844
00:56:15.101 --> 00:56:16.829
You know why we won't work.

845
00:56:17.302 --> 00:56:19.672
Why not. huh?

846
00:56:20.091 --> 00:56:21.904
We're no help to each other.

847
00:56:22.734 --> 00:56:25.183
I have to graduate and get a job.

848
00:56:25.209 --> 00:56:26.119
What's in your heart?

849
00:56:28.466 --> 00:56:29.545
How do you really feel?

850
00:56:43.914 --> 00:56:44.789
Scared.

851
00:56:44.908 --> 00:56:45.787
Scared of what?

852
00:56:49.114 --> 00:56:51.307
Scared I'll have
nowhere to go back to.

853
00:56:52.427 --> 00:56:55.052
If I lose you. I won't have
anywhere left to return to.

854
00:56:55.112 --> 00:56:55.998
Why would you lose me?

855
00:56:58.855 --> 00:56:59.927
If we break up.

856
00:56:59.953 --> 00:57:02.965
we can't go singing
or drinking together.

857
00:57:05.847 --> 00:57:07.369
I can't go to your diner.

858
00:57:29.016 --> 00:57:30.883
I swear I'll be good.

859
00:57:35.308 --> 00:57:36.368
That's it?

860
00:57:37.756 --> 00:57:40.372
What? You need more?

861
00:57:43.428 --> 00:57:45.253
Say you'll give me your heart.

862
00:57:46.049 --> 00:57:48.262
I'll give you my heart.

863
00:58:21.374 --> 00:58:23.202
- Pretty good. huh?
- Totally!

864
00:58:23.289 --> 00:58:24.211
Pay me.

865
00:58:28.169 --> 00:58:30.797
- It's pretty.
- Yeah.

866
00:58:33.389 --> 00:58:34.422
Look over here.

867
00:58:34.505 --> 00:58:35.430
Okay.

868
00:58:37.397 --> 00:58:38.579
Excuse me.

869
00:58:39.218 --> 00:58:41.032
Are you the owner of that Porsche?

870
00:58:41.795 --> 00:58:43.667
- Yes. that's me.
- Right.

871
00:58:43.758 --> 00:58:46.027
I drive the Mercedes over there.
Do you mind moving your car?

872
00:58:46.076 --> 00:58:47.286
My bad.

873
00:58:50.040 --> 00:58:51.947
This is our future house.

874
00:58:53.825 --> 00:58:54.811
There's something here.

875
00:58:55.333 --> 00:58:56.299
Look.

876
00:58:56.386 --> 00:58:57.167
What? Where?

877
00:58:59.146 --> 00:59:00.898
There's more!

878
00:59:02.254 --> 00:59:04.423
- You make curls like this?
- Yeah.

879
00:59:04.492 --> 00:59:06.036
- Twirl it around.
- Like this?

880
00:59:06.682 --> 00:59:07.475
That's it!

881
00:59:07.652 --> 00:59:09.657
- Twirl it fast like this?
- Yes!

882
00:59:10.755 --> 00:59:11.743
It feels good!

883
00:59:11.854 --> 00:59:14.739
I'm with a customer.

884
00:59:14.983 --> 00:59:16.285
- Call me later.
- Great!

885
00:59:21.176 --> 00:59:22.506
What a great story.

886
00:59:22.531 --> 00:59:23.657
What's it about?

887
00:59:35.028 --> 00:59:37.551
"It's a key element
in the notation system."

888
00:59:37.798 --> 00:59:39.296
- Don't sleep.
- Right.

889
00:59:58.284 --> 01:00:00.680
FREE TO TAKE

890
01:00:04.124 --> 01:00:05.226
Are you tired?

891
01:00:07.701 --> 01:00:08.727
- Jeong-won.
- Yeah?

892
01:00:08.830 --> 01:00:10.206
You're pushing. right?

893
01:00:10.968 --> 01:00:12.573
Eun-ho! Jump with me!

894
01:00:12.637 --> 01:00:13.575
No way.

895
01:00:13.711 --> 01:00:15.838
Come on! Get up!

896
01:00:16.480 --> 01:00:17.203
Energy potion!

897
01:00:17.308 --> 01:00:18.758
- What?
- My potion.

898
01:00:23.172 --> 01:00:24.382
All charged!

899
01:00:24.548 --> 01:00:26.755
Good as new!

900
01:00:31.159 --> 01:00:32.245
Hot. isn't it?

901
01:00:33.190 --> 01:00:34.152
Should we get air conditioning?

902
01:00:34.483 --> 01:00:37.148
Install five to get surround cooling?

903
01:00:37.486 --> 01:00:38.545
How about this?

904
01:00:38.637 --> 01:00:41.979
Let's move into the house
I'm building downtown.

905
01:00:42.158 --> 01:00:42.988
Okay.

906
01:00:43.141 --> 01:00:45.803
How about having kids too?

907
01:00:45.866 --> 01:00:46.631
Three?

908
01:00:46.759 --> 01:00:47.614
No!

909
01:00:47.691 --> 01:00:48.455
Why not?

910
01:00:48.809 --> 01:00:51.208
I'm busy with
the Paris Architecture Expo.

911
01:00:55.164 --> 01:00:58.507
Why don't you drop this term
and prepare to transfer?

912
01:01:00.426 --> 01:01:01.628
Major in architecture.

913
01:01:02.366 --> 01:01:04.555
Get your architect license.

914
01:01:05.556 --> 01:01:07.405
Get started.

915
01:01:07.746 --> 01:01:09.421
You can do it!

916
01:01:12.497 --> 01:01:14.348
I can't afford
the tutoring classes.

917
01:01:14.646 --> 01:01:17.612
I'll invest and support you.

918
01:01:18.139 --> 01:01:20.158
But you have to build me
a huge house.

919
01:01:20.281 --> 01:01:22.367
one with a stunning garden.

920
01:01:22.456 --> 01:01:24.163
and my lady over it.

921
01:01:25.537 --> 01:01:26.440
Can you do that?

922
01:01:26.593 --> 01:01:27.226
Yes!

923
01:01:33.767 --> 01:01:35.227
This is nice.

924
01:01:36.763 --> 01:01:37.603
Eun-ho.

925
01:01:37.744 --> 01:01:38.634
Hmm?

926
01:01:38.994 --> 01:01:41.497
Even if we break up.
let's see each other sometimes.

927
01:01:44.021 --> 01:01:45.265
But we're not breaking up.

928
01:01:49.144 --> 01:01:50.110
Come here.

929
01:01:51.111 --> 01:01:52.112
Get some sleep.

930
01:01:53.058 --> 01:01:55.650
Go with the trend.
Why insist on games like this?

931
01:01:56.103 --> 01:01:57.813
Why be so artistic?

932
01:01:59.002 --> 01:02:02.193
This won't sell these days.

933
01:02:02.692 --> 01:02:04.202
TRANSFER PREP ACADEMY

934
01:02:04.286 --> 01:02:05.981
Lee Eun-ho!

935
01:02:10.447 --> 01:02:12.284
Didn't study much?

936
01:02:12.478 --> 01:02:14.529
- Why are you so light?
- I studied!

937
01:02:14.713 --> 01:02:15.839
- Really?
- Yeah.

938
01:02:15.865 --> 01:02:17.260
Then let's take a cab.

939
01:02:17.654 --> 01:02:19.568
Crazy?
Let's just wait for the bus.

940
01:02:20.122 --> 01:02:21.332
No. we can take a cab.

941
01:02:21.762 --> 01:02:22.527
Why?

942
01:02:23.048 --> 01:02:24.661
Did your senior alum
like your game?

943
01:02:24.771 --> 01:02:25.932
He loved it.

944
01:02:26.629 --> 01:02:28.137
so I changed things a bit.

945
01:02:29.047 --> 01:02:31.536
I'll take it to lots of companies.
then choose.

946
01:02:34.247 --> 01:02:35.269
Right.

947
01:02:35.373 --> 01:02:37.967
You'll make it big. Don't worry.

948
01:02:39.030 --> 01:02:40.038
Of course.

949
01:02:41.567 --> 01:02:42.679
Let's take a cab.

950
01:02:44.181 --> 01:02:46.205
Taxi!

951
01:02:48.617 --> 01:02:50.900
Taxi!

952
01:03:01.837 --> 01:03:03.899
Why is it so blurry?

953
01:03:16.055 --> 01:03:18.143
You must've had trouble seeing.

954
01:03:18.474 --> 01:03:20.028
You have diabetes too. right?

955
01:03:20.388 --> 01:03:23.412
Glaucoma can be slowed down.
but it's impossible to cure.

956
01:03:23.439 --> 01:03:25.741
You could lose your eyesight.

957
01:03:26.372 --> 01:03:28.467
Let's do a thorough examination.

958
01:03:33.685 --> 01:03:35.457
Jeong-won!

959
01:03:35.597 --> 01:03:36.440
What?

960
01:03:36.523 --> 01:03:38.398
Do you think you can work
at the show house...

961
01:03:38.440 --> 01:03:40.192
...and study for the TOEIC too?

962
01:03:40.775 --> 01:03:43.528
There are tests every year.
I can take it next year.

963
01:03:43.681 --> 01:03:46.302
Working at the show house counts
as architecture experience too.

964
01:03:46.816 --> 01:03:48.443
This is about my dad.

965
01:03:49.410 --> 01:03:50.539
I'll take care of it.

966
01:03:50.731 --> 01:03:52.441
Stop acting like a stranger!

967
01:03:53.140 --> 01:03:56.045
If I break my leg and can't move.
would you just leave me?

968
01:03:56.083 --> 01:03:58.394
That's totally different.

969
01:03:58.424 --> 01:03:59.506
It's the same!

970
01:04:01.222 --> 01:04:02.932
If I get a job.

971
01:04:03.010 --> 01:04:05.163
I can get a loan. so study.

972
01:04:05.492 --> 01:04:07.473
I don't want you
to quit your game!

973
01:04:07.499 --> 01:04:09.246
I want to help.

974
01:04:09.924 --> 01:04:11.609
What in the world?

975
01:04:11.884 --> 01:04:13.845
Seriously! What in the world!

976
01:04:22.014 --> 01:04:22.914
Are you crying?

977
01:04:24.243 --> 01:04:25.077
No.

978
01:04:25.467 --> 01:04:26.417
Hand.

979
01:04:27.721 --> 01:04:28.878
Touched. huh?

980
01:04:29.127 --> 01:04:30.547
Your eyes are teary.

981
01:04:30.581 --> 01:04:32.191
No! Maybe a little.

982
01:04:34.095 --> 01:04:35.451
A break from school?

983
01:04:36.195 --> 01:04:37.613
- Accepted!
- Pardon?

984
01:04:37.988 --> 01:04:39.448
- Hello.
- Hi.

985
01:04:39.474 --> 01:04:40.516
This is your seat.

986
01:04:41.451 --> 01:04:43.455
RUN AWAY!

987
01:04:45.120 --> 01:04:46.817
Jsonsoft's
"The Angel War Chronicle."

988
01:04:47.116 --> 01:04:49.577
Just copy it enough not to get caught...

989
01:04:49.659 --> 01:04:51.217
...and write a plan for a game.

990
01:04:51.496 --> 01:04:53.331
Copy it. sir?

991
01:04:53.407 --> 01:04:55.388
Welcome.

992
01:04:57.328 --> 01:04:58.621
Jeong-won. here.

993
01:05:00.067 --> 01:05:00.943
How was it?

994
01:05:01.013 --> 01:05:02.389
Something shocking happened.

995
01:05:02.627 --> 01:05:03.584
What?

996
01:05:03.786 --> 01:05:05.128
Hwan-soo told me to...

997
01:05:05.913 --> 01:05:09.535
Speed dial 1 is Eun-ho
and 2 is me.

998
01:05:09.561 --> 01:05:11.183
3 is the village chief.

999
01:05:11.371 --> 01:05:13.629
Put you in number 1
and Eun-ho in 2.

1000
01:05:14.061 --> 01:05:16.236
- Right. I'm first. right?
- Of course.

1001
01:05:18.468 --> 01:05:19.893
I'm home.

1002
01:05:52.010 --> 01:05:53.230
Eun-ho.

1003
01:05:54.652 --> 01:05:55.878
Eun-ho?

1004
01:05:58.949 --> 01:06:00.175
I love you.

1005
01:06:22.355 --> 01:06:23.150
<i>Jeong-won.</i>

1006
01:06:23.686 --> 01:06:24.458
<i>It's Min-jae.</i>

1007
01:06:24.962 --> 01:06:28.371
<i>Our company is taking placements.</i>

1008
01:06:28.765 --> 01:06:29.949
<i>Call me if you're interested.</i>

1009
01:06:38.163 --> 01:06:39.654
Thank you.

1010
01:07:09.711 --> 01:07:11.646
I got the sink clog fixed.

1011
01:07:11.681 --> 01:07:13.850
I paid $90 for it.

1012
01:07:14.444 --> 01:07:16.304
Sure. I'll send you my bank info.

1013
01:07:17.239 --> 01:07:18.925
Renew the lease?

1014
01:07:19.648 --> 01:07:20.399
Of course.

1015
01:07:21.664 --> 01:07:23.172
More deposit?

1016
01:07:23.857 --> 01:07:25.358
Lee Eun-ho!

1017
01:07:30.435 --> 01:07:33.023
I can't decide that by myself.

1018
01:07:33.364 --> 01:07:35.552
I'll talk to my friend...

1019
01:07:36.200 --> 01:07:37.569
...and be in touch.

1020
01:07:42.467 --> 01:07:44.219
Damn it.

1021
01:07:46.298 --> 01:07:47.954
- Hungry?
- Yeah.

1022
01:07:47.994 --> 01:07:48.946
Let's eat.

1023
01:07:49.072 --> 01:07:50.371
Okay.

1024
01:07:52.068 --> 01:07:53.069
Oh. my.

1025
01:07:56.072 --> 01:07:57.274
Why are you so late?

1026
01:07:57.642 --> 01:08:00.256
I got off late because of
a rude customer.

1027
01:08:01.765 --> 01:08:03.215
Not because you met someone?

1028
01:08:03.705 --> 01:08:04.542
Who?

1029
01:08:06.166 --> 01:08:07.261
It's nothing.

1030
01:08:08.098 --> 01:08:09.224
Here. I'll do it.

1031
01:08:09.430 --> 01:08:11.630
I can do it!

1032
01:08:11.761 --> 01:08:13.054
- I'll do it.
- It's okay.

1033
01:08:13.117 --> 01:08:14.618
- You can't.
- I'll do it!

1034
01:08:14.723 --> 01:08:15.742
- Give it.
- I'll do...

1035
01:08:29.134 --> 01:08:30.889
What's the matter with you?

1036
01:08:33.200 --> 01:08:34.389
The landlord...

1037
01:08:35.855 --> 01:08:37.461
...wants to raise the deposit.

1038
01:08:40.952 --> 01:08:42.967
That's why you're stressed?

1039
01:08:43.721 --> 01:08:44.358
Yeah.

1040
01:08:45.040 --> 01:08:46.360
It's okay.

1041
01:08:46.980 --> 01:08:48.815
With you. it doesn't matter where.

1042
01:08:52.624 --> 01:08:53.354
Hmm?

1043
01:09:04.908 --> 01:09:06.117
By the way.

1044
01:09:07.369 --> 01:09:08.346
Jeong-won.

1045
01:09:08.937 --> 01:09:11.050
if I ever bump into you by chance.

1046
01:09:12.164 --> 01:09:13.983
I really wanted to ask you something.

1047
01:09:15.585 --> 01:09:16.384
What is it?

1048
01:09:26.187 --> 01:09:27.355
Hold on.

1049
01:09:34.960 --> 01:09:37.499
<i>Daddy! Why aren't you coming?</i>

1050
01:09:37.546 --> 01:09:38.534
Da-eun!

1051
01:09:38.644 --> 01:09:40.181
<i>Why aren't you here?</i>

1052
01:09:40.362 --> 01:09:43.253
Daddy's airplane got delayed.

1053
01:09:43.559 --> 01:09:44.644
I'm coming tomorrow morning.

1054
01:09:44.970 --> 01:09:46.743
<i>Is it raining there?</i>

1055
01:09:46.905 --> 01:09:48.365
Here? No. it's not.

1056
01:09:48.455 --> 01:09:49.574
<i>Really?</i>

1057
01:09:49.691 --> 01:09:51.806
It's late. Go to bed. sweetie.

1058
01:09:52.293 --> 01:09:55.082
<i>No! Show me the outside.</i>

1059
01:09:55.136 --> 01:09:56.434
Outside?

1060
01:09:56.511 --> 01:09:58.109
<i>Out the window!</i>

1061
01:09:58.138 --> 01:10:00.029
What if it's raining again?

1062
01:10:00.076 --> 01:10:02.355
But it's dark out.

1063
01:10:02.774 --> 01:10:04.275
Show me.

1064
01:10:05.208 --> 01:10:07.605
Show me! Show me!

1065
01:10:08.099 --> 01:10:10.699
Let's go and see it.

1066
01:10:11.714 --> 01:10:12.799
<i>Hurry up!</i>

1067
01:10:12.917 --> 01:10:13.873
Here.

1068
01:10:16.136 --> 01:10:17.554
<i>Oh?</i>

1069
01:10:18.305 --> 01:10:19.270
Look.

1070
01:10:20.340 --> 01:10:21.627
<i>It's all black.</i>

1071
01:10:21.773 --> 01:10:23.086
Right.

1072
01:10:23.462 --> 01:10:25.304
<i>I can't see anything.</i>

1073
01:10:26.271 --> 01:10:27.550
I told you it's black.

1074
01:10:29.108 --> 01:10:30.295
I'll be home tomorrow.

1075
01:10:30.797 --> 01:10:32.159
<i>Okay.</i>

1076
01:10:32.708 --> 01:10:33.668
See you.

1077
01:10:33.723 --> 01:10:35.099
<i>Love you. Daddy.</i>

1078
01:10:35.190 --> 01:10:37.025
I love you. too.

1079
01:10:37.088 --> 01:10:38.631
<i>Daddy kiss!</i>

1080
01:10:40.397 --> 01:10:42.412
<i>You need to kiss too. Daddy.</i>

1081
01:10:43.830 --> 01:10:45.763
<i>Bye! Good night!</i>

1082
01:10:45.798 --> 01:10:46.896
Bye.

1083
01:12:17.436 --> 01:12:18.503
Ouch.

1084
01:12:26.960 --> 01:12:27.970
Hold on.

1085
01:12:28.768 --> 01:12:30.019
Try lifting this side?

1086
01:12:30.068 --> 01:12:31.628
That's it.

1087
01:12:34.169 --> 01:12:35.368
It won't work.

1088
01:12:35.600 --> 01:12:37.227
- I think it can go in.
- No way.

1089
01:12:37.627 --> 01:12:38.761
Just throw it out.

1090
01:12:39.112 --> 01:12:41.183
Move over. Let me try.

1091
01:12:41.691 --> 01:12:42.608
Come on.

1092
01:12:50.165 --> 01:12:52.953
- Ouch!
- Why you!

1093
01:12:53.191 --> 01:12:54.652
Look how big it is!

1094
01:12:54.678 --> 01:12:55.531
It won't fit!

1095
01:12:55.712 --> 01:12:56.894
Don't be stubborn.

1096
01:12:59.849 --> 01:13:01.558
Damn.

1097
01:13:02.227 --> 01:13:03.325
I'll get the ointment.

1098
01:13:05.257 --> 01:13:07.656
It's okay. I'll get it.

1099
01:13:16.707 --> 01:13:17.840
<i>Coming for Thanksgiving?</i>

1100
01:13:18.070 --> 01:13:19.668
I can't.

1101
01:13:20.502 --> 01:13:21.642
I'm busy at work.

1102
01:13:22.929 --> 01:13:23.832
I need to go.

1103
01:13:29.254 --> 01:13:30.638
Jeez.

1104
01:13:34.094 --> 01:13:35.011
Finished?

1105
01:13:35.359 --> 01:13:36.686
You gave it to me yesterday.

1106
01:13:37.534 --> 01:13:39.403
Though it's copying.
it takes time. sir.

1107
01:13:39.558 --> 01:13:42.414
Instead of submitting
trash like this.

1108
01:13:42.658 --> 01:13:44.396
you could've finished it!

1109
01:13:44.875 --> 01:13:45.606
Look.

1110
01:13:45.786 --> 01:13:47.885
I want to make cool games too.

1111
01:13:48.289 --> 01:13:50.299
You're not the only one
who wants to look cool!

1112
01:13:50.325 --> 01:13:52.612
But we can't. so we don't!

1113
01:13:52.745 --> 01:13:56.018
If you want to make money.
shut up and do what you're told.

1114
01:13:59.752 --> 01:14:01.440
Why? Don't want to do it?

1115
01:14:02.615 --> 01:14:03.630
Stand up.

1116
01:14:04.890 --> 01:14:06.892
Get up. you prick!

1117
01:14:07.274 --> 01:14:08.484
Sir!

1118
01:14:09.381 --> 01:14:12.925
How dare you glare at me.
you crazy prick!

1119
01:14:13.092 --> 01:14:14.677
Aren't you going to apologize?

1120
01:14:14.807 --> 01:14:16.831
Let go of me! Say you're sorry!

1121
01:14:16.985 --> 01:14:17.759
Say you're sorry!

1122
01:14:17.785 --> 01:14:19.702
Sorry. sir. I apologize.

1123
01:14:21.713 --> 01:14:23.575
- Let go!
- I'm sorry.

1124
01:14:30.764 --> 01:14:32.317
Why didn't you pick up the phone?

1125
01:14:33.642 --> 01:14:36.524
It's okay. Text me later. Bye.

1126
01:14:39.446 --> 01:14:40.423
Who was it?

1127
01:14:41.297 --> 01:14:42.301
Kyung-seok.

1128
01:14:43.298 --> 01:14:44.257
Give me that.

1129
01:14:57.667 --> 01:15:00.190
Aren't you too busy to come here?

1130
01:15:01.129 --> 01:15:02.407
He took the day off work.

1131
01:15:02.483 --> 01:15:04.746
The company can't run without him.
Don't worry.

1132
01:15:04.785 --> 01:15:06.692
SORRY. I HAVE NO EXTRA MONEY EITHER

1133
01:15:06.775 --> 01:15:08.476
NEVER MIND

1134
01:15:10.883 --> 01:15:15.345
Any plans to settle down
and get married?

1135
01:15:17.718 --> 01:15:21.087
You're out of fashion these days
if you get married early.

1136
01:15:21.505 --> 01:15:22.756
Just thought I'd ask.

1137
01:15:23.423 --> 01:15:27.726
But if you start saving together...

1138
01:15:28.172 --> 01:15:30.131
You got it all wrong. Dad.

1139
01:15:31.028 --> 01:15:32.871
Who gets married without
a house these days?

1140
01:15:33.775 --> 01:15:35.838
And Jeong-won may not want to.

1141
01:15:41.453 --> 01:15:42.145
Oh!

1142
01:15:42.221 --> 01:15:44.724
I made beef bone soup
that Jeong-won likes.

1143
01:15:44.904 --> 01:15:45.693
Wait here.

1144
01:15:46.464 --> 01:15:48.029
It's okay. really.

1145
01:15:55.901 --> 01:15:57.528
Don't test my patience.

1146
01:15:58.217 --> 01:15:59.332
Don't take it. then.

1147
01:16:03.410 --> 01:16:04.372
Sir!

1148
01:16:04.883 --> 01:16:07.136
- I dropped it.
- Oh. no!

1149
01:16:11.634 --> 01:16:13.080
I told you to close the shop!

1150
01:16:13.768 --> 01:16:16.228
How can you cook
with your eyes like that!

1151
01:16:18.773 --> 01:16:19.677
Move!

1152
01:16:20.601 --> 01:16:21.873
Who asked you to help?

1153
01:16:57.307 --> 01:16:58.328
Lee Eun-ho!

1154
01:17:00.221 --> 01:17:01.519
Quit that damn company.

1155
01:17:01.826 --> 01:17:03.354
Report it to the Ministry of Labor.

1156
01:17:03.871 --> 01:17:05.267
What about the bills?

1157
01:17:05.329 --> 01:17:08.089
Go back to making your game
or work for a real game company!

1158
01:17:08.115 --> 01:17:10.536
Just do anything but this!

1159
01:17:11.620 --> 01:17:12.577
Jeong-won.

1160
01:17:13.371 --> 01:17:15.026
That's what I want to say to you.

1161
01:17:15.986 --> 01:17:17.368
Did you give up on architecture?

1162
01:17:17.875 --> 01:17:19.717
Love that show house job?

1163
01:17:20.234 --> 01:17:21.204
Then keep at it.

1164
01:17:21.875 --> 01:17:23.250
Who says I love it?

1165
01:17:24.342 --> 01:17:26.525
I'm working there for you.

1166
01:17:36.550 --> 01:17:39.289
Don't say that you're doing it for me!

1167
01:17:40.435 --> 01:17:42.228
You heard from Min-jae.
didn't you?

1168
01:17:42.702 --> 01:17:44.812
He said he'd help you
with a placement. didn't he?

1169
01:17:45.553 --> 01:17:46.581
Just do that.

1170
01:17:48.638 --> 01:17:50.146
I won't stop you.

1171
01:17:50.413 --> 01:17:53.226
I did get that text.
but I didn't reply.

1172
01:17:53.408 --> 01:17:54.491
Call him and do it.

1173
01:17:56.340 --> 01:17:58.058
Don't blame me later.

1174
01:17:58.371 --> 01:17:59.121
just do it.

1175
01:18:03.466 --> 01:18:04.467
Aren't you coming?

1176
01:18:08.521 --> 01:18:09.814
You doubted me?

1177
01:18:34.937 --> 01:18:36.835
No. that's not it.

1178
01:18:40.374 --> 01:18:43.294
I didn't mean that. I'm so sorry.

1179
01:18:43.940 --> 01:18:46.164
There's nothing
I can do for you now.

1180
01:18:46.282 --> 01:18:47.498
Let go.

1181
01:18:52.713 --> 01:18:53.891
Come on.

1182
01:18:54.371 --> 01:18:55.803
That's not it.

1183
01:18:55.890 --> 01:18:56.683
Stop!

1184
01:18:56.908 --> 01:18:59.845
Look at me.
Please! I'm really sorry.

1185
01:18:59.984 --> 01:19:01.816
I made a big mistake.

1186
01:19:01.861 --> 01:19:05.830
I must've lost my mind.
What a crazy jerk.

1187
01:19:07.499 --> 01:19:08.583
Eun-ho!

1188
01:19:09.848 --> 01:19:13.660
I hate that I'm crying more ever...

1189
01:19:13.743 --> 01:19:15.131
...since I started seeing you.

1190
01:19:15.347 --> 01:19:18.552
Jeong-won. Look at me. I'm sorry.

1191
01:19:21.391 --> 01:19:23.226
Jeong-won. please.

1192
01:19:23.356 --> 01:19:25.705
I'm sorry. Why did I say that?

1193
01:19:26.143 --> 01:19:27.360
I'm sorry. Jeong-won.

1194
01:19:29.579 --> 01:19:31.497
I'm exhausted. Eun-ho.

1195
01:19:51.080 --> 01:19:52.540
RUN AWAY!

1196
01:19:52.992 --> 01:19:57.079
<i>Applicants for the civil service
examination are at an all-time high.</i>

1197
01:19:57.220 --> 01:19:58.805
<i>Ministry of Public Administration states...</i>

1198
01:19:58.831 --> 01:20:01.968
<i>...the average competition rate
is around 82.1 to 1.</i>

1199
01:20:02.453 --> 01:20:08.383
<i>Education administration
is the highest at 583.8 to 1.</i>

1200
01:20:08.884 --> 01:20:09.740
NEW HIRE INTERVIEWS

1201
01:20:09.870 --> 01:20:10.935
Mr. Jung Hong-jin.

1202
01:20:11.094 --> 01:20:12.846
Yes. I made it to the final round.

1203
01:20:12.936 --> 01:20:14.270
I see.

1204
01:20:16.475 --> 01:20:19.387
EUN-HO

1205
01:20:20.328 --> 01:20:22.119
- I love the cabinets.
- Nice. huh?

1206
01:20:22.161 --> 01:20:24.462
I want a place like this.

1207
01:20:24.984 --> 01:20:27.194
- And put furniture like this?
- Let's move to the next room.

1208
01:20:39.874 --> 01:20:42.575
HANSUNG GAMES:
YOU HAVE NOT BEEN SELECTED

1209
01:20:46.687 --> 01:20:48.946
TEST ADMISSION TICKET

1210
01:20:58.144 --> 01:21:00.746
ERIC AND JANE'S HISTORY

1211
01:21:02.412 --> 01:21:03.584
What do you think?

1212
01:21:05.991 --> 01:21:07.581
It's nice...

1213
01:21:07.952 --> 01:21:09.689
But why does the plot feel so flat?

1214
01:21:10.260 --> 01:21:12.637
It'd be more fun with some crisis.

1215
01:21:13.471 --> 01:21:15.223
Everyone says the same thing.

1216
01:21:15.793 --> 01:21:17.403
I keep hearing that kind of comment.

1217
01:21:18.192 --> 01:21:19.415
but I don't want...

1218
01:21:19.888 --> 01:21:21.140
...to make stories like that.

1219
01:21:21.265 --> 01:21:24.149
Still. a good story needs
the character to struggle a bit.

1220
01:21:28.424 --> 01:21:30.037
- Eun-ho.
- What?

1221
01:21:31.359 --> 01:21:33.195
Though it may seem boring.

1222
01:21:33.223 --> 01:21:34.389
let's live peacefully.

1223
01:21:46.319 --> 01:21:49.281
CITY RECYCLING

1224
01:21:49.662 --> 01:21:52.302
What happens if Eric can't find Jane?

1225
01:21:52.615 --> 01:21:53.923
It'll be a sad ending.

1226
01:21:54.904 --> 01:21:55.836
Well...

1227
01:21:58.909 --> 01:22:00.291
Then the world turns black and white.

1228
01:22:40.702 --> 01:22:42.875
You're good at finding me.

1229
01:22:49.746 --> 01:22:53.736
You always run away
just enough for me to find you.

1230
01:22:56.010 --> 01:22:58.276
I didn't run away. I left.

1231
01:23:04.957 --> 01:23:06.320
Why did we break up?

1232
01:23:19.959 --> 01:23:21.961
Is this on sale for 1 plus 1?

1233
01:23:23.295 --> 01:23:24.199
Yes.

1234
01:23:26.675 --> 01:23:27.773
Eun-ho!

1235
01:23:28.795 --> 01:23:30.101
- What?
- Hey!

1236
01:23:30.653 --> 01:23:31.576
Eun-ho!

1237
01:23:31.867 --> 01:23:33.104
- Hey!
- Hey!

1238
01:23:45.318 --> 01:23:46.588
Jeong-won!

1239
01:23:46.852 --> 01:23:49.496
Hi!

1240
01:23:49.549 --> 01:23:52.064
What's with the uniform?

1241
01:23:52.090 --> 01:23:52.990
It's good to see you.

1242
01:23:53.016 --> 01:23:55.201
Cheers!

1243
01:23:55.284 --> 01:23:57.048
I had no idea
whiskey tasted this good.

1244
01:23:57.074 --> 01:23:58.342
Eat all you want.

1245
01:23:58.576 --> 01:24:00.198
I got lots there.

1246
01:24:00.421 --> 01:24:02.256
Your place is nice.

1247
01:24:02.534 --> 01:24:03.614
Do you own it?

1248
01:24:03.653 --> 01:24:06.156
It's in my name.
but my parents bought it.

1249
01:24:06.288 --> 01:24:07.519
I'm drowning in debt.

1250
01:24:07.606 --> 01:24:10.067
Look. I brought this.

1251
01:24:10.702 --> 01:24:13.619
- Cover model!
- Hey!

1252
01:24:14.704 --> 01:24:17.181
- When did you bring that?
- It's his dad.

1253
01:24:17.221 --> 01:24:20.045
You're a chef?
You couldn't even make ramyeon.

1254
01:24:20.488 --> 01:24:23.658
I'm just a figurehead.

1255
01:24:24.433 --> 01:24:25.578
My dad is the real boss.

1256
01:24:25.660 --> 01:24:29.205
I just go and look around the restaurant.

1257
01:24:29.664 --> 01:24:31.093
I'm sick of living like a loser.

1258
01:24:31.120 --> 01:24:32.447
Still. I'm so jealous!

1259
01:24:32.473 --> 01:24:34.868
- Don't take it for granted.
- Right.

1260
01:24:35.622 --> 01:24:36.960
- Eun-ho.
- Yeah?

1261
01:24:37.541 --> 01:24:38.834
- Come here.
- Okay.

1262
01:24:39.697 --> 01:24:41.747
It's been so long. Join in.

1263
01:24:41.788 --> 01:24:43.069
First time seeing
the Han River view.

1264
01:24:43.484 --> 01:24:44.651
- Nice. huh?
- Yeah.

1265
01:24:45.410 --> 01:24:48.081
I heard seeing the river view
for too long can be depressing.

1266
01:24:49.956 --> 01:24:51.958
Remember our club room?

1267
01:24:52.333 --> 01:24:54.525
- Bullizard!
- Bullizard!

1268
01:24:55.101 --> 01:24:56.338
Make $10 million!

1269
01:24:56.376 --> 01:24:59.364
- That was just crazy.
- Right.

1270
01:24:59.390 --> 01:25:01.859
You can't make $10 million
by making games.

1271
01:25:01.885 --> 01:25:05.195
But we had ambition and passion!

1272
01:25:05.335 --> 01:25:07.796
- Only because we were young. man.
- Right.

1273
01:25:07.871 --> 01:25:09.706
- Clueless.
- But it was fun.

1274
01:25:12.042 --> 01:25:14.412
Eun-ho? Do you want to
grab one more drink?

1275
01:25:14.635 --> 01:25:15.803
- Another one?
- Yeah.

1276
01:25:16.498 --> 01:25:17.561
Let's go!

1277
01:25:25.917 --> 01:25:27.633
Are you mad about something?

1278
01:25:28.928 --> 01:25:29.762
No.

1279
01:25:31.534 --> 01:25:32.944
You seem like it.

1280
01:25:38.980 --> 01:25:40.607
That uniform...

1281
01:25:42.032 --> 01:25:43.668
Don't wear that aside from work.

1282
01:25:43.694 --> 01:25:45.118
They'll look down on you.

1283
01:25:57.624 --> 01:25:59.484
Why aren't you
developing your game?

1284
01:26:14.184 --> 01:26:15.143
Eun-ho.

1285
01:26:17.943 --> 01:26:20.060
You'll make it big.

1286
01:26:20.972 --> 01:26:22.140
I know it.

1287
01:26:27.698 --> 01:26:29.654
Can you please stop saying that?

1288
01:26:35.713 --> 01:26:37.107
Did you do that on purpose?

1289
01:26:37.261 --> 01:26:38.247
What the hell?

1290
01:26:39.450 --> 01:26:40.215
What?

1291
01:26:40.447 --> 01:26:41.674
I was just sitting!

1292
01:26:45.501 --> 01:26:46.436
Son of a gun!

1293
01:26:46.469 --> 01:26:48.069
Get lost!

1294
01:26:48.152 --> 01:26:50.196
- Come here!
- Jerk!

1295
01:26:50.235 --> 01:26:52.613
- He hit me first!
- Son of a gun!

1296
01:26:53.106 --> 01:26:55.077
What's wrong with you!

1297
01:26:55.485 --> 01:26:58.164
Let go! Damn it!

1298
01:26:59.610 --> 01:27:02.276
What the heck did I do wrong!
I did nothing!

1299
01:27:02.372 --> 01:27:04.291
Why me!

1300
01:27:04.417 --> 01:27:07.399
I was staying still! Why hit me!

1301
01:27:10.458 --> 01:27:12.665
If you want to hit someone.
just hit me!

1302
01:27:53.170 --> 01:27:54.397
Hello.

1303
01:27:55.936 --> 01:27:57.883
Sorry. we couldn't go this time.

1304
01:27:58.000 --> 01:28:00.628
<i>It's okay. Don't worry.</i>

1305
01:28:00.780 --> 01:28:02.911
<i>I called Eun-ho several times.</i>

1306
01:28:02.937 --> 01:28:04.097
<i>but he didn't answer.</i>

1307
01:28:06.831 --> 01:28:09.058
He must've been busy.

1308
01:28:10.862 --> 01:28:12.931
Applying for jobs takes work.

1309
01:28:13.934 --> 01:28:16.239
He went to study now too.

1310
01:28:16.438 --> 01:28:17.664
<i>Alright.</i>

1311
01:28:18.012 --> 01:28:20.657
<i>Take care. Jeong-won.</i>

1312
01:28:21.540 --> 01:28:23.525
We'll go down for Thanksgiving.

1313
01:28:24.181 --> 01:28:25.988
- <i>See you.</i>
- Bye.

1314
01:28:41.672 --> 01:28:43.643
CHEER UP. EUN-HO

1315
01:28:53.146 --> 01:28:54.696
CHEER UP. EUN-HO

1316
01:28:55.576 --> 01:28:57.494
They said it'll rain today.

1317
01:33:05.177 --> 01:33:06.168
Jeong-won.

1318
01:33:06.479 --> 01:33:07.531
Eun-ho.

1319
01:33:08.644 --> 01:33:11.333
I forgot the past and you did too.

1320
01:33:12.338 --> 01:33:14.455
We're both much better off now.

1321
01:33:17.295 --> 01:33:18.296
I know.

1322
01:33:30.099 --> 01:33:31.351
But what if...

1323
01:33:32.922 --> 01:33:35.435
...we didn't move to that old house.

1324
01:33:37.246 --> 01:33:38.495
Would we still be together?

1325
01:33:47.077 --> 01:33:47.994
No.

1326
01:33:50.107 --> 01:33:52.176
We would've stayed together
for a year or so.

1327
01:33:53.889 --> 01:33:55.318
Then what if...

1328
01:33:56.517 --> 01:33:57.990
...you waited for me?

1329
01:34:00.744 --> 01:34:02.287
If you waited for me till the end?

1330
01:34:05.053 --> 01:34:08.460
Then you wouldn't have
finished your game.

1331
01:34:08.988 --> 01:34:09.906
Then...

1332
01:34:11.561 --> 01:34:15.419
What if we just got married?

1333
01:34:17.207 --> 01:34:18.797
We would've gotten divorced.

1334
01:34:19.102 --> 01:34:20.937
That's enough. Eun-ho.

1335
01:34:21.772 --> 01:34:23.182
Wait! Just one more.

1336
01:34:23.629 --> 01:34:24.802
Just one last question.

1337
01:34:29.181 --> 01:34:30.125
That day...

1338
01:34:33.389 --> 01:34:34.790
What if I got on the train?

1339
01:34:37.275 --> 01:34:38.540
What if I stopped you?

1340
01:34:46.160 --> 01:34:47.758
Then...

1341
01:34:57.490 --> 01:35:00.124
I would've stayed with you.

1342
01:35:01.578 --> 01:35:02.750
Forever.

1343
01:35:26.153 --> 01:35:28.597
No. We would've
broken up eventually.

1344
01:35:32.186 --> 01:35:33.637
Because...

1345
01:35:37.714 --> 01:35:40.366
You let the fan blow only on you.

1346
01:35:41.633 --> 01:35:42.816
How petty.

1347
01:36:01.224 --> 01:36:02.298
I...

1348
01:36:04.088 --> 01:36:05.691
I let you slip away.

1349
01:36:11.471 --> 01:36:12.998
I let go of you.

1350
01:36:16.024 --> 01:36:17.877
No. we...

1351
01:36:19.177 --> 01:36:21.048
...let each other go.

1352
01:36:26.500 --> 01:36:29.253
And it was the right choice.

1353
01:36:31.555 --> 01:36:33.427
I don't regret it. Eun-ho.

1354
01:37:19.884 --> 01:37:21.510
KIMCHI. SQUID DISH

1355
01:37:22.205 --> 01:37:24.763
<i>Romance movies always frustrate me.</i>

1356
01:37:26.357 --> 01:37:27.606
CHEER UP. EUN-HO
<i>They're like fools...</i>

1357
01:37:27.640 --> 01:37:29.866
<i>...who only wake up after it's over.</i>

1358
01:37:31.138 --> 01:37:32.674
<i>I was one of them.</i>

1359
01:37:34.482 --> 01:37:37.478
<i>Still. I believed someday
I could make things right.</i>

1360
01:37:37.867 --> 01:37:39.175
<i>So I held on.</i>

1361
01:37:39.605 --> 01:37:40.989
<i>hoping I could fix things.</i>

1362
01:37:48.052 --> 01:37:48.899
Jane...

1363
01:37:48.956 --> 01:37:51.805
...is a good wizard who manages
all the colors in this world.

1364
01:37:51.831 --> 01:37:54.050
- Okay.
- But the demon king takes Jane.

1365
01:37:54.281 --> 01:37:55.322
Then what?

1366
01:37:55.463 --> 01:37:56.823
The colors are gone.

1367
01:37:58.631 --> 01:37:59.958
<i>Now. it's the final stage.</i>

1368
