1404
01:42:31.154 --> 01:42:32.524
I have something to say.

1405
01:42:35.333 --> 01:42:36.541
Back then.

1406
01:42:40.080 --> 01:42:43.000
thank you for being my home.

1407
01:42:44.174 --> 01:42:45.078
Eun-ho.

1408
01:43:26.726 --> 01:43:28.408
Take care. then.

1409
01:43:31.739 --> 01:43:32.663
By chance.

