1414
01:44:36.968 --> 01:44:38.201
Goodbye.

1415
01:44:40.400 --> 01:44:41.801
Goodbye.

1416
01:45:29.331 --> 01:45:31.317
FROM LEE EUN-HO

1417
01:45:34.862 --> 01:45:37.246
DEAR JEONG-WON

1418
01:45:51.087 --> 01:45:52.078
<i>Jeong-won.</i>

1419
01:45:55.300 --> 01:45:56.464
<i>how are you?</i>

1420
01:46:02.933 --> 01:46:06.187
<i>You come to mind
around this time every year.</i>

1421
01:46:07.792 --> 01:46:10.969
<i>I ended up making your favorite
dishes again this year.</i>

1422
01:46:13.528 --> 01:46:14.452
<i>Recently.</i>

1423
01:46:14.952 --> 01:46:18.094
<i>I heard from Eun-ho
that you two broke up.</i>

1424
01:46:20.708 --> 01:46:23.100
<i>I loved seeing you
enjoying my food.</i>

1425
01:46:24.489 --> 01:46:25.983
<i>Now. I have no way to share it.</i>

1426
01:46:31.889 --> 01:46:33.199
<i>It'd be great...</i>

1427
01:46:33.278 --> 01:46:35.417
<i>...if relationships could last forever.</i>

1428
01:46:36.107 --> 01:46:39.910
<i>but it's hard not to
let each other down.</i>

1429
01:46:42.536 --> 01:46:45.928
<i>People's feelings and lives
are bound to change.</i>

1430
01:46:50.316 --> 01:46:51.593
<i>But that's okay.</i>

1431
01:46:54.069 --> 01:46:55.307
<i>It's truly okay.</i>

1432
01:47:09.809 --> 01:47:16.107
<i>I don't know
if you'll ever get this letter.</i>

1433
01:47:19.422 --> 01:47:21.160
<i>but please know...</i>

1434
01:47:21.946 --> 01:47:23.941
<i>...that you were dear to me and to Eun-ho.</i>

1435
01:47:28.064 --> 01:47:29.759
<i>No matter what choices you make...</i>

1436
01:47:31.412 --> 01:47:33.082
<i>...and how you live.</i>

1437
01:47:34.939 --> 01:47:36.676
<i>I know you'll do well. Jeong-won.</i>

1438
01:47:37.519 --> 01:47:38.471
<i>Do you understand?</i>

1439
01:47:42.879 --> 01:47:44.031
<i>Wherever you are.</i>

1440
01:47:44.699 --> 01:47:46.973
<i>make sure to eat well.</i>

1441
01:47:48.127 --> 01:47:51.507
<i>If you ever want
some of my cooking.</i>

1442
01:47:51.624 --> 01:47:52.791
<i>come by anytime.</i>

1443
01:47:55.864 --> 01:47:58.749
<i>Stay healthy and happy.</i>

1444
01:48:15.281 --> 01:48:19.127
WOULD YOU LIKE TO SEE THE ENDING?

1445
01:49:11.548 --> 01:49:13.957
<i>I forgot my wish long ago.</i>

1446
01:49:15.558 --> 01:49:16.960
<i>What I remember is...</i>

1447
01:49:18.326 --> 01:49:20.278
<i>...that we had dreams then.</i>

1448
01:49:21.739 --> 01:49:23.683
<i>That we made wishes together.</i>

1449
01:49:25.382 --> 01:49:26.951
<i>That once we were us.</i>

1450
01:49:56.220 --> 01:50:00.141
KOO KYO HWAN

1451
